game.name: Cartoon Cars Spot the Difference
game.description:
Sometimes different games are very tricky and challenge your brain to a great extent. Are you ready to enter such kind of mind-boggling difference challenge and show off the world that you are the biggest difference finder? Join Cartoon Cars Spot The Difference and be prepared to find out some differences between the car images with the similar looks! Find all the five differences between similar cartoon cars to clear the present level and move to the advanced level!

When you click the play button, you would see three similar cartoon car images on the screen. These differences can be on any of these three car bodies. Check out their windows, luggage stands, tyres, gate locks, car bonnets or all the other parts that look pretty different from the other similar car image! You move to the next level when you spot all the five differences. In the next level, you would see two red and green cartoon car images. Look at them carefully to spot all the differences and clear the present level!

In all the rest levels, you have to spot differences by putting your difference-finding and sharp reflexes abilities. Use your arrow keys or mouse to play this html5 puzzle challenge on your desktop! Tap or swipe the screen to enjoy this fun challenge on your mobile phone or tablet! In case of seeking more funny and challenging difference puzzles, you can check out website and know what kind of online game suits your gaming needs the most.
